latest_valid_value.value:
C Condensing with LN2.
C Assumes that the cryostat is cold enough.
C v2.5, uses temperatures and new heater control. Uses temperature channel names.
C v2.5, uses detection of turbo2. stops pumping VC.
C To be used with Software version 1.4-130 or higher.

START

STATE 1
SET_STATE 400

STATE 400 Detect the presence of extra Turbo
IF option_turbo==1
OFF turbo2
SET_STATE 401
WAIT 3
ELSE 
SET_STATE 402
ENDIF

STATE 401 Close critical valves, stop pumping VC with turbo2.
C Make sure critical valves are closed, start circulation
OFF v15
OFF v17
OFF v18
OFF v3
OFF v11
OFF v12
OFF v13
OFF v8
OFF v4
OFF v21
OFF v14
OFF v16
OFF v22
OFF v23
OFF scroll2
OFF turbo2
OFF turbo1
C Start circ. through trap and comp. (40X).
ON v9
ON v7
ON v6
ON compressor
ON v5
ON scroll1
SET_STATE 403
WAIT 10

STATE 402 Close critical valves, stop pumping VC.
C Make sure critical valves are closed, start circulation.
OFF v15
OFF v17
OFF v18
OFF v3
OFF v11
OFF v12
OFF v13
OFF v8
OFF v4
OFF v21
OFF v14
OFF v16
OFF scroll2
OFF turbo1
C Start circ. through trap and comp. (40X).
ON v9
ON v7
ON v6
ON compressor
ON v5
ON scroll1
SET_STATE 403
WAIT 10

STATE 403 Start circ
ON v10
ON v2
SET_STATE 404
WAIT 60
C Delay for opening gate valve.

STATE 404 Start circ
ON v1
OFF v2
SET var3=p5
SET_STATE 410

STATE 410 High tank pressure condensing
C High tank pressure condensing (41X).
IF p5>250
SET_STATE 411
ELSE
SET_STATE 420
ENDIF

STATE 411 High p5 condensing
IF p4<600
ON v12
OFF v10
SET var4=time
SET_STATE 412
WAIT 0.5
ELSE
ON v10
OFF v12
C Confirmation opening v10 and closing V12.
SET_STATE 410
WAIT 10
ENDIF

STATE 412 High p5 condensing
IF ((time-var4)>180)&&(p5>300)
OFF v12
ON v10
ERROR Needle valve set too tight!
ELSE
SET_STATE 413
ENDIF

STATE 413 High p5 condensing
IF (time-var4)>180
OFF v12
ON v10
SET_STATE 410
ELSE
SET_STATE 414
ENDIF

STATE 414 High tank pressure condensing
IF p4>900
OFF v12
ON v10
SET_STATE 415
WAIT 10
C Delay to recover p5 undershoot.
ELSE
ON v12
C Confirmation opening V12.
SET_STATE 412
WAIT 0.5
ENDIF

STATE 415
C Close hs-mc.
IF p5<(var3-80)
C var3 set to p5 at start of condensing.
C when MXC is hotter than still, no need to switch off HS-ST
OFF hs-mc
SET_STATE 416
ELSE
SET_STATE 410
ENDIF

STATE 416
C Close hs-still 
IF (p5<(var3-80)&&(tstill<(t4k+2)))
C var3 set to p5 at start of condensing.
OFF hs-still
SET_STATE 410
ELSE
SET_STATE 410
ENDIF

STATE 420 Low p5 condensing
C Low tank pressure condensing (42X).
OFF v12
C Confirmation closing V12.

IF p5>50
SET_STATE 421
ELSE
SET_STATE 430
ENDIF

STATE 421 Low p5 condensing
IF p4<600
ON v11
OFF v10
SET_STATE 422
WAIT 0.5
ELSE
ON v10
OFF v11
C Confirmation opening v10 and closing V11.
SET_STATE 420
WAIT 10
ENDIF

STATE 422 Low p5 condensing
IF p4>900
OFF v11
ON v10
SET_STATE 420
WAIT 10
C Delay to recover p5 undershoot.
ELSE
ON v11
C Confirmation opening V11.
SET_STATE 422
WAIT 0.5
ENDIF

STATE 430 Pump tank empty
C Empty tank.
ON v11
OFF hs-still
OFF hs-mc
SET_STATE 431
WAIT 420

STATE 431 Pump tank empty
OFF v11
SET_STATE 440

STATE 440 Start circ
C Start circulation (44X).
OFF compressor
SET_STATE 441

STATE 441 Start circ
IF p3<1000
OFF v5
OFF v6
SET_STATE 442
ELSE
SET_STATE 441
WAIT 2
ENDIF

STATE 442 Start circ
IF p3<p4
ON v4
SET_STATE 443
WAIT 180
ELSE
SET_STATE 442
WAIT 2
ENDIF

STATE 443 Start circ
IF p3<700
ON turbo1
SET_STATE 444
WAIT 1200
C Delay time to apply still heat.
ELSE
SET_STATE 443
WAIT 5
ENDIF

STATE 444 
ON ext
C Apply default still heating.
SET_STATE 500

STATE 500
STOP

END


C v1.1 confirmation OFF v11 and v12 added (411, 421).
C v1.2 confirmation ON V11 and v12 added (414, 422).
C v1.2 confirmation ON V10 (411, 421).
C v1.2 wait time start turbo from 900s to 180s (442).
C v1.2 HS switchpoint -80mbar
C v1.23 Comments modified
C v1.23 Time to let turbo spin down added (300)
C v1.24 Close all before starting circ.
C v1.24 Check for tank pressure (422)
C v2.01 state 415 and 416 switch off HSs one by one if temperatures allow it
C       state 430 pumping tank empty 7min instead of 5min
C v2.03 Stop pumping VC when closing critical valves:
C       State 401 off v21, 22, 23, 16, 14, v4 
C v2.11 removed T6.
C v2.12 HSS OFF forced at 430
C v2.5  detects turbo2. Uses temperature channel names.
C v2.51 close critical valves before condensing.
